<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bn">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>For You...</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Great+Vibes&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        .font-cursive { font-family: 'Great Vibes', cursive; }
        .font-serif { font-family: 'Lora', serif; }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        .animate-fade-in { animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-out forwards; }

        .letter-paper {
            background-color: #fffdf9;
            background-image: radial-gradient(#f0e8d5 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 20px 20px;
        }

        @keyframes floating {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }
        .flower-float { animation: floating 4s ease-in-out infinite; }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 via-rose-50 to-orange-100 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4 sm:p-8">

<main class="letter-paper max-w-2xl w-full rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden border border-amber-100/50 animate-fade-in relative">

<div class="h-2 w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-300 via-amber-400 to-orange-300"></div>

<div class="p-8 sm:p-12 md:px-16">

<div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
<div class="relative group flower-float">
<img src="https://i.postimg.cc/wMzbnqwS/file-000000007f5071fa8698e0f7e09518dc.png"
class="w-full max-w-[320px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg border-4 border-white object-cover">
</div>
</div>

<h1 class="text-center font-cursive text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-amber-600 mb-10">
This bouquet of flowers is for You 🌻
</h1>

<div class="font-serif text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-6">

<p>
Since you gave me “The Great Gatsby” 📖, I felt it’s my duty to give you a book too… 😅  
But since my knowledge about books is almost negative 📚❌, I tried to get the one that was already in your cart… 🛒
</p>

<p>
Asa kori je tor ei gift ta pochondo hoyeche… 💛  
Sudhu ekta kotha bolar ache…  
<i>"Ekta kotha bolte bolte life er chapter e page berei choleche…”</i> 📖  
Jai hok…
</p>

<p>
Jeta ami bolte chachilam seta bolar age…
</p>

<p class="bg-rose-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
Ami jani na tui exactly kano block korechis… 😔  
Jodi eta naam ta na bolar jonno hoye thake… then I am extremely, infinitely sorry… 🙇‍♂️💔
</p>

<p>
Ami oi din bari chilam na… Ami didi r laptop kinte gechhilam tokhon tui message koris… 💻  
Baire thakar jonno ami tokhon sathe sathe reply korte pari ni…
</p>

<p>
Tui notice o korbi ami type korchilam… ⌨️  
Kintu send korte pari ni, karon puro lekha ta complete hoyni…
</p>

<p>
And besides that, ami bhabini je tor eto kharap lagbe… 😞
</p>

<p>
Tai age Sneha ke jigesh korechilam…  
Sudhu ei jonno je toke na janai, aar tor kosto na hoy…
</p>

<p>
Kintu she kichu bole ni…  
Ar ami amar emotions control korte pari ni bole directly toke jigesh korechi…
</p>

<p class="bg-amber-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
For this… I am realllllllyyyyyy sorryyyyyy… 🙏💔  
Sotti bolchi… onekta…
</p>

<p>
Ami sudhu toder moto manush der harate chai na… 🥺  
Tai majhe majhe bhul bhal kaj kore pheli…
</p>

<p>
Tor jodi mone hoy je block korei rakhbi… That’s up to you… 😞
</p>

<p>
Kintu ekta request… ignore maris na please… 🙏 Plssss…
</p>

<p>
Tui amake bujha amar bhul ta… Ami chup chap shune bujhe nebo…
</p>

<p class="text-center font-medium text-rose-500">
But please… don’t do this to me… 🥺
</p>

<hr class="my-6">

<p>
Ar aita chara… aar ekta jinis—
</p>

<p>
Last 2 years… ⏳  
Ami jani na amra eksathe thakbo kina…  
Kintu ami amar 100% debo jate ei bonding ta kokhono na bhenge jai… 🤝  
Tarpor ja hobar seta hobei…
</p>

<p>
Ato din tor sathe ja kotha hoyeche chat e…  
Sotti bolte ami onekta Dip er sathe jerokom kotha boli, serokom i bolechi…  
Ar samnasamni to… chere i de… 😅  
Nervousness at its peak thake tokhon… 😶‍🌫️
</p>

<p>
Ami toke like kori… tui o seta janis… ❤️  
Ar ami ei jinis ta kokhono mon theke sorate parbo na…
</p>

<p>
Tar mane emon noi je ami toke pressure dichi… ❌  
Na na, erokom kokhono bhabis na please… 🙏
</p>

<p>
Tor jodi kokhono mone hoy je—  
“Ha, cheleta bhalo… Trust kora jabe… Sob kichu share kora jabe… And he will not judge…”
</p>

<p class="text-center">
Tahole sudhu amake ekbar bolis… 🙂
</p>

<p>
Besi ami ar bhaat bokbo na… 😅 Eta amar moner kotha chilo…
</p>

<p>
Last 2 years jeno amra ei bonding ta aro strong kori… 💫  
Friends hisebe hok ba jai kichu hok…
</p>

<p class="text-center font-semibold text-amber-700">
Sudhu ekta jinis— Bhalo bhabe last 2 years ta enjoy kori… 🌻
</p>

<p class="text-center mt-6 text-xl font-cursive text-amber-600">
Lastly… Bhalo thakis… 🌻💛
</p>

</div>
</div>
</main>

</body>
</html>
